room_title: Escape room "Escape Jack The Ripper" by MindEscape in Philadelphia
room_description:
It is the autumn of 1888, roaming the streets of London’s east end is the notorious serial killer “Jack the Ripper.” His shadow of terror sweeps through the dark cobblestone streets and alleys of one of the darkest slums in London.
You are a group of detectives that were tasked to find out the identity of the serial killer. After accepting the mission, you go out with your group to a local pub and are offered a drink by a mysterious stranger.
Next thing you know, you wake up to darkness with little recollection of how you got there.
